text: Raamatukogu is an Estonian magazine published in Tallinn, Estonia by Estonian Librarians Association and Estonian National Library. First number was issued in 1923. 1964-1967 it was issued under the name "Huvitavat raamatukogude tööst". ==References== ==External links== *About magazine, Estonian Librarians Association's website Category:Magazines published in Estonia Category:Library science magazines
